-quality image reconstruction from real-world Bayer pattern data collected\nby NASA Mars Curiosity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Nov 2019 22:01:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 2020 20:32:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 4 Aug 2020 00:21:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-05"}
