ently reported for the Milky Way, making this a\nplausible scenario for the formation of the Galactic thick disc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 9 Nov 2019 15:45:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Feb 2020 14:19:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-12"}
